{"tid":1026360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心噏！公廁成清潔工「飯堂」　網民轟政府外判種禍？","createTime":"2019-02-18T05:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T16:01:04.000Z","uid":225464,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e4c16970bf03c162db9f209c4b36ce0eadc0ba","tid":1026360,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>心噏！公廁成清潔工「飯堂」 網民轟政府外判種禍？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SGiKsI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SGiKsI&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=59a55efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SGiKsI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190218/photo/bkn-20190218124201023-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190218130257\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190218124201023-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190218130257&h=d451ab33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解決生理需要的公廁竟成清潔工的用膳場所。<br />\n<br />\n一餐「安落茶飯」都難求？近日有清潔工在公廁內用膳，有市民見狀百感交集，直呼︰「心酸」。<br />\n<br />\n網民Chow Chowchi上周六（16日）上載照片，指在旺角一間公廁內，見到一名身穿藍色制服的清潔工以洗手盆作枱，打開飯盒正在用饍。他看着膠椅上微駝着背的身影，不禁感嘆︰「香港點解會搞成咁」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友批評政府外判工作剝削基層︰「有點樣嘅政府就有點樣嘅社會」、「希望政府多多照顧老人啦」、「畀咗判頭做就算，冇人監管，老人家肯去做唔攞綜援，自力更生搞成咁，政府盲X咗」、「睇到好心噏」。"},{"pid":"ee727928470cad5b12233408a639e8d7bf72a48f","tid":1026360,"uid":51720,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"網民肯定冇睇《開心速遞》 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0c47e4afdf3efa9fc3939cd70109769e196384","tid":1026360,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":41,"score":-41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"acb96b2e9917094c9aa5cb89713a9d19b8b86beb","tid":1026360,"uid":10692,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b4a817c2a2675048aeb494491e34651